Package: mtban
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: MikroTik address-list manager via REST API
 Manages MikroTik firewall address-list entries via the RouterOS REST
 API (RouterOS 7+). Supports ban, unban, and timed entries via
 MikroTik's built-in timeout. Uses only Go standard library, no external
 dependencies.
